high_descs: Walk to the counter on the right side of the fridge.
Pick up the butter knife by the salt on the counter.
Walk to the left, face the fridge.
Slice the bell pepper in the top part of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Slice the bell pepper in the fridge.

high_descs: Take the butter knife from the counter
Turn around, head to the fridge
Open the fridge, cut off part of the red pepper, close the door
anns.task_desc: Take the butter knife from the counter, cut off part of the red pepper in the fridge

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen table on the left.
Grab the knife off the table.
Walk to the fridge with a tomato in it.
Remove the stem of the tomato inside the fridge with a knife.
anns.task_desc: Use a knife to remove the stem of a cooled tomato.
